          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1683890935148-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1683890935148-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1683890935148-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is browning, add your<strong> fresh orecchiette</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook your <strong>orecchiette</strong> for 4-6 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
