    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once your orecchiette is cooked with a slight bite, add your <strong>spinach </strong>to the pot and cook for a further 20-30 secs or until wilted</p><p>Once wilted, drain the <strong>orecchiette and spinach</strong>, reserving a cup of<strong> starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1683890948298-x200.jpg",
