    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has thickened, add the<strong> drained orecchiette and spinach </strong>and give everything a good mix up until the pasta is coated in the sauce – this is your <strong>creamy Tuscan-style chicken sauce with fresh orecchiette</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
      "order": 7,
